d5609.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/fd1eeeae-b73b-47c6-a0da-16968771a74e.png\"/><br><img src=\"https://asset.moon.vn/img/chat/large/2026/1/98c95836-8515-4afe-a7a2-43e8cb361a35.jpg\" data-filename=\"\" style=\"max-width: 600px; height: auto;\">",
